ashi and a filmography of Japanese horror films currently available in the UK and US."  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aHorror filmszJapanxHistory and criticism. 4aFilm, Media & Cultural Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh1 aBolton, Christopher, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrophy, Philip, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aConrich, Ian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEvans, Gareth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGoldberg, Ruth, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHand, Richard J., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHantke, Steffen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHills, Matt, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLafond, Frank, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLewis, Graham, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMcRoy, Jay, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSharrett, Christopher, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWhite, Eric, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWilliams, Tony, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEdinburgh University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-2000z97831107804680 cprintz978074861994840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978147447093340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781474470933423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781474470933/original  a978-3-11-078046-8  Edinburgh University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2013-2000c2000